|-
|'''[[Male]]''' || ''He'' laughed || I hit ''him'' || ''His'' face bled || I am ''his'' || He shaves ''himself''
|-
|'''[[Female]]''' || ''She'' laughed || I hit ''her'' || ''Her'' face bled || I am ''hers'' || She shaves ''herself''
|-
|'''[[It (pronoun)|It]]''' || ''It'' laughed || I hit ''it'' || ''Its'' face bled || I am ''its'' || It shaves ''itself''
|-
|'''[[Ve (pronoun)|Ve]]''' || ''Ve'' laughed || I hit ''ver'' || ''Vis'' face bled || I am ''vis'' || Ve shaves ''verself''
|}

